description:
With the premiere of the brand new Rush Hour (March 31st) series, Karlous invited his homie and star of the show Justin Hires to the 85 South Show, who happened to be with his homie Justin Mitchell. All 3 got their comedy start in the A and do a lot of catching up. Tune into Rush Hour March 31st! Listen to the show, leave a comment(on iTunes) and subscribe!
